{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2503603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1. 大三专业课又多又难，没精力在保证GPA不掉的情况下修通识课。\n2. 只有修够一定学分的通识课才有保研资格", "timestamp": 1631595161, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2503662, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": 2503603, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 啊？保研还有通识课学分要求吗？这个要在哪看啊", "timestamp": 1631595565, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2503681, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "通识课很多简单容易刷分，而且早上完早结束", "timestamp": 1631595706, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2503717, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "主要是担心通识课会占用一些时间精力，影响专业基础课的学习", "timestamp": 1631595865, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2503731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": 2503681, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 早早上完大四不就没事干了", "timestamp": 1631595935, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504251, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不可行，通识课学分很多，大四可能选不够；一学期上一两门通识课应该不会对专业课的学分绩有什么影响", "timestamp": 1631601321, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": 2504251, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 甚至有些通识课可以帮助你提高总gpa", "timestamp": 1631601369, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504372, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 477830, "reply_to": 2503662, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 大多数院系保研要求是修完指导性教学计划里大一到大三的所有课程（最多少1~2门课程），通识课程在大一到大三的课程要求中，建议自查自己院系的培养方案和教学计划", "timestamp": 1631602708, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 477830, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "通识都留到大三大四修可行吗？\n为什么身边的同学们都要在大一大二学很多通识课啊？", "timestamp": 1631594814, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631602709, "url": "", "vote": {}}}